    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Drawable>, java.util.Collection<Drawable>, java.util.List<Drawable>, java.util.RandomAccess

    public class VectorOfDrawables
extends java.util.Vector<Drawable>
    Contains all Drawable type objects (ClassDiag & RelationshipDiag) in a Vector, to allow universal use by the system as required.
    Author:
    Connor Goddard (clg11), Sam Jackson (???), Craig Hepinsthall (???)
